setWorkflowIds.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller does have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the set workflow ID is zero
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the set workflow ID is not zero
      ├─ when the set workflow ID is the same as the one already configured
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the set workflow ID is different than the one already configured
         ├─ it should set the new workflow ID
         └─ it should emit a WorkflowIdSetEvent
